overview: Osama bin Laden eluded U.S. forces for nearly 10 years after September 11, 2001. Efforts to kill him have ranged wide over the years as the Taliban regime crumbled. At 1:10 a.m. May 1, 2011, local time in Pakistan, a secret U.S. special operations team lands in the Pakistani compound housing bin Laden and conducts a raid.
title: Killing Bin Ladden
